[I] UML modeler and UML diagram tool

[T] Umbrello is a Unified Modelling Language (UML) modelling tool and code
[T] generator. It can create diagrams of software and other systems in the
[T] industry-standard UML format, and can also generate code from UML diagrams
[T] in a variety of programming languages.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/umbrello/

[A] The KDE-Team
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/office extra/desktop/kde
[F] CROSS OBJDIR

[L] GPL
[V] 26.04.0

